      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a showroom-quality find. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and no chips or scratches, while the interior remains in pristine, like-new condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, the car is perfect; the engine and transmission perform exactly as they did the day it left the factory, and all electronic features and systems function flawlessly. For a buyer seeking a vehicle that has been meticulously preserved and maintained to the highest possible standard, this car offers a rare opportunity to own a virtually new example of this model.",
