      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "$17,500 - Ready for a reliable workhorse? This car is a fantastic opportunity for someone who prioritizes function and value! It has served its previous owners well and shows some honest cosmetic wear and signs of use, but it remains a solid choice for your daily commute or as a dependable secondary vehicle. If you're looking for a budget-friendly ride that's ready to get the job done, this is the one for you!",
