      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in a state of absolute preservation, mirroring its original showroom delivery. Every surface, from the hand-finished interior to the flawless exterior paintwork, reflects a standard of care reserved for the most discerning collectors. Mechanically synchronized to perfection and boasting a documented history of fastidious maintenance, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a definitive example of the marque.",
      "price": 48500.0,
